channel.title: Code for a Check Bank command..?
channel.description:
Hey people..
Well, i am looking for a checkbank command.
One that when your ie, i log in on an Administrator, and type ::checkbank PLAYERSNAME eithe that players bank comes up on MY screen, or, the items that are in that players bank and the amount of them are sent to me ( you know, like through the chatbox or something)..
ANY ONE Who can help would be considered a rockin' rockstar to me.. :)
So yeah. Please help me out As Soon As Possible.
Jube.
